Welcome to the Mamnuts talker code.

I should make a better instalation guide, I know, but for now let's just say 
this:

To compile the talker you must:

$ cd src
$ make
$ make install

Now, in the main directory of the talker you have a binary called 'mamnuts'.
Just do

$ ./mamnuts 

to run it.

Feel free to ask any questions sending an e-mail to Marcos.Marado@sonae.com .

